  ${
    $d x y z R $.
    $( Any relation is founded on the empty set. $)
    fr0 $p |- R Fr (/) $=
      ( vx vz vy c0 wfr cv wss wne wa wbr cab cin wceq wrex wi dffr2 wn ss0
      nne sylibr imnan mpbi pm2.21i mpgbir ) EAFBGZEHZUFEIZJZUFCGDGAKCLMENDUFOZ
